For 0.6 the process of production has changed.


== Backend
1. Compile the backend into backend/dist
2. Ensure that the .env file is present and up to date.
3. Ensure that the pm2 json config on the server is up to date
   - pm2 delete evotempus.backend
   - pm2 start evotempus-pm2.json

This will bring up the backend on port 3001 using pm2.

== App
1. Compile the app into app/build
2. Take down the nginx server if running
3. Copy the nginx.conf.evotempus to /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
4. Copy the contents of app/build to the /usr/share/nginx/html directory.
5. Start the nginx server.
